OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry with variable cloud on
OL,7,FWednesday and Thursday. Some sunny
OL,8,Fintervals on Friday and breezy along
OL,9,Fthe coast. Temperatures remain warm
OL,10,Fbut feeling cooler along the coasts.
